### API Gateway Test Requests
### Base URL: http://localhost:8000

### Gateway Health Check
GET http://localhost:8000/health

### All Services Status
GET http://localhost:8000/api/status

### API Documentation
GET http://localhost:8000/api/docs

### Customer Service - Signup (through Gateway)
POST http://localhost:8000/api/customer/customers/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "John",
  "lastName": "Doe",
  "email": "john.doe@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "confirmPassword": "password123",
  "phone": "+1234567890"
}

### Customer Service - Signin (through Gateway)
POST http://localhost:8000/api/customer/customers/signin
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "john.doe@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Seller Service - List Sellers (through Gateway)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/sellers/sellers/list

### Products Service - List Products (through Gateway)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/products/products
Content-Type: application/json

### Products Service - Create Product (through Gateway)
POST http://localhost:8000/api/products/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test Product",
  "description": "A test product created through API Gateway",
  "price": 29.99,
  "category": "Electronics",
  "sellerId": "seller123",
  "stock": 100,
  "tags": ["test", "electronics"]
}

