### Orders Service - Get Cart (through Gateway) - Requires Auth Token
GET http://localhost:8000/api/orders/cart
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### Admin Service - Dashboard Stats (through Gateway)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/admin/dashboard/stats

### Admin Service - Services Health (through Gateway)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/admin/services/health

### Notifications Service - Send Email (through Gateway)
POST http://localhost:8000/api/notifications/send
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "template": "welcome",
  "recipient_email": "test@example.com",
  "recipient_name": "Test User",
  "data": {
    "name": "Test User",
    "welcome_message": "Welcome to our platform!"
  }
}

### Error Test - Non-existent Route
GET http://localhost:8000/api/nonexistent/test

### Error Test - Service Down (assuming service is down)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/customer/customers